## 学术来源声明 (Academic Attribution)

本软件 (丰容 / Skill Enrichment, formerly Skill-Aware Reflection) 工程化自以下论文:

  Ju, Ruofei, Wang, Xinrui, Ding, Xin, Yang, Yifan, Wu, Hao, Jiang, Shiqi,
  Zhang, Qianxi, Wen, Hao, Li, Xiangyu, Wang, Meijun, Li, Kun, Liu, Yunxin,
  Dai, Haipeng, Wang, Wei, and Cao, Ting. 2026.
  "EmbodiSkill: Skill-Aware Reflection for Self-Evolving Embodied Agents."
  arXiv preprint arXiv:2605.10332.

核心方法论 (四类反思框架、S = (S_body, S_app) 结构、分类逻辑)
由上述论文作者提出,本仓库的贡献在于工程化实现与领域应用转换。

